text.tspan: The Law of the Spirit of Life
For that which the law could not do, being weak,
In the flesh, God sending His Son,
In the likeness of flesh, and concerning sin,
He condemned sin in the flesh.
That the righteous requirement of the law
Who do not walk according to the flesh of sin
But who walk according to the spirit.
For those who are according to the flesh,
They all mind the things of the flesh;
But those who are according to the spirit,
Mind the things of the Spirit.
